# Image Folder Structure

Place your images in the appropriate folders:

## /services
- Service card images (Apps, Web, Automations, Marketing)
- Recommended size: 800x600px or larger
- Format: WebP or JPG

## /work
- Project/portfolio images
- Recommended size: 1920x1080px (full-screen)
- Format: WebP or JPG

## /testimonials
- Client avatars/photos
- Recommended size: 200x200px (square)
- Format: WebP, PNG, or JPG

## /why-us
- Images for "Why Us" section features
- Recommended size: 600x400px
- Format: WebP or JPG

## /hero
- Hero section background or decorative images
- Recommended size: 1920x1080px or larger
- Format: WebP or JPG

## /about
- About section images
- Recommended size: varies
- Format: WebP or JPG

---
Usage in code: `/images/services/app-image.webp`
